Option Explicit

'when the Lesson1 button is clicked, this sub is executed.
Private Sub ButtonLesson1_Click()
    UserFormWelcome.Hide                        'hide the welcome userform (popup window)
    UserFormLesson1.StartLesson                 'UserFormLesson1 is the form for the first lesson. StartLesson is the name of the sub (aka sub procedure).  We're telling Excel to run the code found there.
End Sub

